node.text: @erickanicolemalone “Dreams From The Edge” is a sweet and subtle short film revealing how one’s faith or lack of faith in Dreams crosses many generations. Special thanks to @thelmaofgoodtimes, @rosemarklane @therealmarkcurry and @alexiafaith1700 for helping my simple vision come to life. Had an opportunity to make a cameo in this film with the incredibly talented Rose Mark Lane so excited for her future. Loved this cast and the journey. #dreamsfromtheedge #newshortfilm #filmfestivalgem #blackstories #creativecontent #filmfestivalwinner #filmfestivalnominations @niagarafestival

node.text: Tesla has suspended vehicle purchases using #Bitcoin, concerned about the rapidly increasing use of fossil fuels for mining transactions. At CurrencyWorks™ we are also concerned about the cost to the environment as it relates to Bitcoin mining. This is why #CurrencyWorks designed and implemented Zer00 crypto, a scalable #crypto mining operation sustained with zero-cost energy. @trytoncapitalpartners @film2air @currencyworks @cameronchell
